      .span6
        h3 Free and Open
        p Whether it's contributing code, reporting bugs, or fostering your own project, the advantages of leveraging and contributing to the open source community are undeniable. Don't be a relic of the past and ignore the amazing opportunities that free and open source brings. Having troubles getting started? Contact us today and we will help you move forward.
        h3 Meetups
        p You are likely to find us at a local meetup such as <a href="http://www.meetup.com/vancouver-javascript-developers/">VanJS</a> or the <a href="http://www.meetup.com/erlang-vancouver/">Vancouver Erlang Group</a>. We also organize the Node Brigade. If you have a talk idea or would like to contribute funds for space rental, please reach out to us.
