          img(src="img/node-brigade-logo-500px.png", width="100%;")
      .span5.offset1
        h3
          a(href="http://phonegap.com") PhoneGap
        p Now renamed as Cordova and brought into the Apache family, PhoneGap was invented and authored by Brock Whitten and Rob Ellis to bring device functionality and cross platform development into the hands of open web technologists.
        h3
          a(href="http://xuijs.com") XUI
        p After PhoneGap was created it was quickly realized current DOM manipulation libraries were not sufficient under the constraints of mobile devices. Championed by Rob Ellis in 2009, XUI remains a goto tool for many applications and laid the foundation for alternatives such as ZeptoJS.
        h3
          a(href="https://github.com/sintaxi/node-dbox") dbox
        p Dbox is a NodeJS SDK for the official Dropbox API. It abstracts the irrelevant detail of speaking to a REST API while exposing the bits that are important, such as status code and body.